thread.title: Vernon Lesser
thread.title_full: Logo Influx reviewed by Vernon Lesser

author: Vernon Lesser
title: Vernon Lesser
text: I did the business package with Logo Influx and they designed some exceptional logos the first go round. I picked one that I feel will represent my business for the long term future. I've had other logos designed in the past that were more expensive and less original. Good company to work with.
